  "title": "✨ Corporate Sales Partner — Growth, Exposure & Travel Opportunities ✨",
  "description": "<p>Looking to build your corporate career with flexibility, uncapped earnings, and real growth opportunities? Join us as a <strong>Corporate Sales Partner</strong>, where you’ll represent established organisations and engage directly with corporate customers across Singapore.<br /></p><p>This role is highly interactive — you’ll meet business owners, decision-makers, and management teams at their offices, developing strong communication and business relationship skills from day one.<br /></p><p>✨<strong> What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct face-to-face meetings with corporate clients</li><li>Visit client offices to introduce business solutions and services</li><li>Build and maintain professional corporate relationships</li><li>Network with industry contacts and expand your client base</li><li>Work closely with the sales team to achieve shared targets</li></ul><p></p><p>🎓<strong> Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Training provided for those new to sales</li><li>Confident, outgoing, and enjoys meeting people</li><li>Strong communication & interpersonal skills</li><li>Self-driven, independent, and eager to grow</li><li>Comfortable with a face-to-face engagement role</li></ul><p></p><p>🚀<strong> What You’ll Gain</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Structured training & mentorship</strong> to develop professional communication and sales skills</li><li><strong>Career progression</strong> — potential to advance to Team Leader for strong performers</li><li><strong>Overseas travel opportunities</strong> for top achievers</li><li>Flexible, dynamic, and growth-focused environment</li><li>Opportunity to work with reputable organisations </li></ul><p></p><p>🌱<strong> Why This Role?</strong></p><p>You enjoy flexibility while building valuable corporate experience. You’ll gain business exposure that accelerates your professional development and opens doors to future leadership roles.<br /></p><p><strong>Ready to build a high-growth career with flexibility and rewards? Apply now! </strong>🚀</p>",
